Aspire
Fund:

The $50 Million Challenge

     “With this gift, we will help prepare University of Houston students
     to thrive in the global marketplace. Strong faculty leadership is
     paramount to the University’s success. This new wave of outstanding
     faculty will build upon the University’s already exceptional
     faculty. We believe that this investment will continue the process
     of motivating students and benefit our great city of Houston through
     work in the classrooms, institutes and labs.

     Anonymous Donor

   brick-arrow-bar.svg Learn More

